About

About

We Are All About Community A successful and thriving community has a strong backbone of businesses that help move things toward a better future. By being a part of the Chamber you are leaving a positive imprint on your local community. Collaboration With over a thousand businesses across every industry you can tap into our network of resources and knowledge to find the solution to literally any business challenge you are facing. Leadership Come and meet the business representatives that you want to do business with by participating in some of the over 100 Chamber exclusive programs and events happening each year. The Chamber Team Stephen Lewis President & CEO Carrie Acosta Executive Assistant and Office Manager Amy Cervantes Membership Sales Manager Artena Greene Government and Community Relations Manager Brenda Oliver Administrative Assistant Amy Pryor Events & Sponsorship Manager Lynn Ramsey Member Relations Coordinator

Signature Events Our signature events take place once a year (or more) and hundreds of attendees show up to enjoy the fun festivities.

Signature Events

Big Orange Awards The Big Orange Awards is an annual awards ceremony that celebrates the accomplishments and triumphs of some of the Chamber‚Äôs most admired and inspirational members. Learn More Celebrating Extraordinary Women Be inspired, empowered, and connect! Listen to the experiences of some of West Orange County‚Äôs leading businesswomen at Celebrating Extraordinary Women. Learn More Best Fest Best Fest ‚Äì Taste of West Orange is the largest food and beverage tasting, and business expo of West Orange, with over 1200 attendees. Guests can indulge in a variety of delicious food and beverage offerings from some of the best local restaurants, bars, caterers, and breweries that West Orange County has to offer. Learn More Topical Luncheon Series This event series gives attendees the opportunity to hear updates from our municipalities, county government and transportation in West Orange County. Learn More The Stina D‚ÄôUva Tour de Chamber Over 100 riders, assemble in the Hamlin town Center of Horizon West for a fun-filled, casual ride that ends at a brewery for good eats and beverages. Learn More Annual Golf Classic Tee it up while strenghtning your connections in the West Orange community! Bring your best clients, top prospects, and office staff for a fun afternoon of relationship building on the fairway. Learn More Member Celebration Celebrate our West Orange Chamber members at the Member Celebration and the annual Passing of the Gavel. Learn More Windermere Wine & Dine The West Orange Foundation‚Äôs premier fundraising event, Windermere Wine & Dine is more than just an evening of culinary delight‚Äîit‚Äôs a celebration of community spirit and purpose that furthers the Foundation‚Äôs ability to give back to the community. Learn More Hob Nob and Straw Poll This annual non-partisan event gives you an opportunity to meet the candidates who will appear on the 2026 ballot. Learn More
